data.description: SELLER OFFERING $5,000 IN CONCESSIONS FOR BUYER CLOSING COSTS, RATE BUY DOWN ETC.!!!  DON'T WAIT TO BUILD!!  Welcome home to this move in ready, lovely Jemison model with 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 full baths.  A front porch welcomes you into this one-story all concrete block home. The design seeks to optimize living space with an open concept kitchen that overlooks the versatile great room with high ceilings and covered lanai. The well-appointed kitchen features an island with bar seating, oversized walk in pantry and sleek stainless steel appliances. The owners bedroom is located at the rear of the home for privacy and has an en suite bathroom with a double vanity and spacious walk-in closet providing substantial storage space. A second bedroom and bathroom are located at the front of the home. Just off the kitchen, the versatile flex space can be utilized as an office or cozy den or 3rd bedroom. There is an indoor laundry room and  2 car garage.  Rear and side neighbors have already installed a fence so it won't take much to complete the fence on your property.  Completely repainted inside.  Window blinds on all windows and ceiling fans stay with the home. HOA fee in beautiful Victoria Oaks also includes…Spectrum TV Select plan, Fiber Internet with Wifi, and lawn irrigation. Amenities include a zero entry swimming pool, fitness center, playground, beach volleyball, walking trails, and more.  This one won't last long!
